                "112 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The scattered protons were momentum analysed",
                "in a magnetic spectrometer were detected in a",
                "scintillation counter hodoscope with 16 energy channels",
                "The polarization measurements for elastically scattered",
                "protons were carried out by a polarimeter with carbon",
                "as the second scatterer."
              ]
            }
          ],
